CustomField.description: The API name, including namespace, of the field on the Assignment object you want to use as the assignment bill rate in forecasting calculations. If left blank, the value in the Bill Rate field is used.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The API name, including namespace, of the field on the Assignment object you want to use as the assignment bill rate in forecasting calculations. If left blank, the value in the Bill Rate field is used.
CustomField.label: Assignment Bill Rate Field
